 &lt;p&gt;⭐️&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://leetcode.com/problems/minimum-common-value/description/?envType=daily-question&amp;amp;envId=2024-03-09&#34;&gt;&lt;ins class=&#34;dot&#34;&gt;題目敘述&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Given two integer arrays  &lt;code&gt;nums1&lt;/code&gt;  and  &lt;code&gt;nums2&lt;/code&gt; , sorted in non-decreasing order, return &lt;em&gt;the &lt;strong&gt;minimum integer common&lt;/strong&gt; to both arrays.&lt;/em&gt; If there is no common integer amongst  &lt;code&gt;nums1&lt;/code&gt;  and  &lt;code&gt;nums2&lt;/code&gt; , return  &lt;code&gt;-1&lt;/code&gt; .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that an integer is said to be &lt;strong&gt;common&lt;/strong&gt; to  &lt;code&gt;nums1&lt;/code&gt;  and  &lt;code&gt;nums2&lt;/code&gt;  if both arrays have &lt;strong&gt;at least one&lt;/strong&gt; occurrence of that integer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-1&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-1&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 1&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input:&lt;/strong&gt; nums1 = [1,2,3], nums2 = [2,4]&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output:&lt;/strong&gt; 2&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Explanation:&lt;/strong&gt; The smallest element common to both arrays is 2, so we return 2.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 2&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input:&lt;/strong&gt; nums1 = [1,2,3,6], nums2 = [2,3,4,5]&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output:&lt;/strong&gt; 2&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Explanation:&lt;/strong&gt; There are two common elements in the array 2 and 3 out of which 2 is the smallest, so 2 is returned.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;解題思路&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#解題思路&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 解題思路&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;solution&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#solution&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Solution&lt;/h2&gt;
